title: Catalan Independence: Fighting Franco's Ghost (Part 2)
description:
Our previous report looked at how the current deadlock between Madrid and Catalonia share battlelines with the conflict between the left and right. 

In this second episode, Belal Awad of redfish talks to Catalans who see the surge in support for independence as a chance to begin organising for an alternative future.

Additional footage courtesy of ACN
